<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">国风·唐风·羔裘</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonef013ab2a099">
<p>羔裘豹祛，自我人居居。岂无他人？维子之故。<br />羔裘豹褎，自我人究究。岂无他人？维子之好。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="tool">
<div class="shoucang"><iframe style="width:18px; height:30px; border:0px;" src="/shiwen2017/like.aspx?idsw=118&from=http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=ef013ab2a099"></iframe></div>
<div class="toolpinglun"><a href="javascript:copy(118)"><img id="copyimg118" src="/img/copy.png" alt="复制" width="18" height="18" /></a></div>
<div class="toolpinglun" style=" cursor:pointer;" onmouseover="madeweixin('118','https://m.gushiwen.org/shiwenv_ef013ab2a099.aspx')" onmouseout="outweixin(118)"><img id="weixinimg118" src="/img/weixin.png" / alt="" width="18" height="18"/></div>
<div class="toolpinglun"><a href="/xiefanyi.aspx?shiID=118"><img src="/img/write.png" / alt="" width="18" height="18"/></a></div>
<div class="toolpinglun" style=" margin-top:-4px;"><a href="/randShowNew.aspx?id=5673"><img src="/img/bootmright.png" alt="下一首" width="26" height="26" /></a></div>
